; M3 gate: dynamic value slots (driver.md §6.4). The host sets slots via the
; SET_VAL mailbox command (see m3-dynval.cmds.json); the stream reads them at
; dispatch time. Exercises PARAM_FROM_VAL (:tl4 $amp), PARAM_ADD_VAL (:tl4+ $amp),
; PARAM_MUL_VAL (:vol* $fac), PARAM_MUL (static :vol* 2.0), the $time source
; (:ar1 $time), and a mid-stream SET_VAL that the last note reads back.
(def-val amp 24 0..127)
(def-val fac 256 0..1024)
(fm1 :tempo 150 :alg 4 :fb 3 :ar1 31 :tl1 20 :ar4 31 :tl4 8 :len 4
  :tl4 $amp   c
  :tl4+ $amp  e
  :vol* $fac  g
  :vol* 2.0   c
  :ar1 $time  e
  :tl4 $amp   g)
